    },
    {
      "start": 873.14,
      "end": 874.64,
      "text": "둘 다 모르는 상황이었습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 874.64,
      "end": 876.3,
      "text": "아, 본인이 말이 놓고 까먹었네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 876.3,
      "end": 876.62,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 876.62,
      "end": 877.9,
      "text": "아, 왠지 오늘은"
    },
    {
      "start": 877.9,
      "end": 878.74,
      "text": "퇴장하실 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 878.74,
      "end": 879.72,
      "text": "제가 탭댄스라도"
    },
    {
      "start": 879.72,
      "end": 881.88,
      "text": "좀 추는 척이라도 해봐야 되나"
    },
    {
      "start": 881.88,
      "end": 884.1,
      "text": "I would love to see a demonstration"
    },
    {
      "start": 884.1,
      "end": 885.06,
      "text": "Show it to me"
    },
    {
      "start": 885.06,
      "end": 885.84,
      "text": "10번 보여주세요"
    },
    {
      "start": 885.84,
      "end": 886.94,
      "text": "아유, 죄송합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 886.94,
      "end": 887.8,
      "text": "아유"
    },
    {
      "start": 887.8,
      "end": 888.86,
      "text": "그러면 내용 한 번 더"
    },
    {
      "start": 888.86,
      "end": 889.36,
      "text": "들어볼게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 889.36,
      "end": 891.32,
      "text": "She said she really enjoyed"
    },
    {
      "start": 891.32,
      "end": 892.12,
      "text": "meeting you yesterday"
    },
    {
      "start": 892.12,
      "end": 894.1,
      "text": "And I must say"
    },
    {
      "start": 894.1,
      "end": 895.48,
      "text": "you did quite a little number on her"
    },
    {
      "start": 895.48,
      "end": 896.46,
      "text": "I did?"
    },
    {
      "start": 896.68,
      "end": 897.1,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 897.1,
      "end": 898.08,
      "text": "You convinced her"
    },
    {
      "start": 898.08,
      "end": 898.96,
      "text": "that you knew how to dance"
    },
    {
      "start": 898.96,
      "end": 899.7,
      "text": "and you were really good"
    },
    {
      "start": 899.7,
      "end": 900.54,
      "text": "at tap dancing"
    },
    {
      "start": 900.54,
      "end": 901.74,
      "text": "Oh, me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 902.42,
      "end": 902.74,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 902.74,
      "end": 904.54,
      "text": "Well, what did she say?"
    },
    {
      "start": 905.02,
      "end": 905.78,
      "text": "She said she hoped"
    },
    {
      "start": 905.78,
      "end": 907.48,
      "text": "you'd give her a demonstration one day"
    },
    {
      "start": 907.48,
      "end": 909.81,
      "text": "It's funny"
    },
    {
      "start": 909.81,
      "end": 912.19,
      "text": "I didn't know"
    },
    {
      "start": 912.19,
      "end": 913.51,
      "text": "I knew how to tap dance"
    },
    {
      "start": 913.51,
